arStrings.szText: Casting {c_important}Golem{/c}'s active Skill creates a bond between you for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. While the bond is active, both of you are {c_important}{u}Unhindered{/u}{/c} and gain {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1%|]{/c} Movement Speed.
Casting {c_important}Golem{/c}'s active Skill grants Movement Speed and {c_important}{u}Unhindered{/u}{/c}.
